Package com.example.networkmeup.domain

Class TIN

java.lang.Object
com.example.networkmeup.domain.TIN
public class TIN extends Object
The TIN class represents a Tax Identification Number (TIN) and validates its format and check digit. It ensures the TIN meets specific criteria for a valid format and check digit validation.
